{"tid":1229933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先串到老豆無聲出..有D過意唔去","createTime":"2019-06-16T05:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T12:10:21.000Z","uid":149494,"like":141,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5e34cb47a24164e732f7073cfc13d7ab01a96ad7","tid":1229933,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"TVB播緊送中相關新聞<br />\n我︰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; 老豆︰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(對住我老母講)︰聽聞有D有錢佬係咁比錢D人出黎示威喎, 咩大瘤嗰D<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰大瘤一早轉咗軚撐修例啦, 關咩事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰轉咗咩，D人話佢身有屎所以有份派錢架喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(大聲)︰佢一早話支持政府修訂逃販條例啦，咪鬼屈啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰總之有人收錢搞事啦，聽聞衝去前排嗰班有5000收, 有相影哂<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰收5000就企前排比差佬開槍射？不如我比5000你衝出去好無？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰咁佢地估唔到差佬會開槍架嘛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰係囉, 又會開槍既, 而家林鄭又唔認係佢落order喎, 一層推一層, 推到落前線警員到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰幾大唔認啦, 認咗又激到你班友出黎反得仲勁d<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰下，但我聽聞而家搞到好多差佬士氣低落咋喎，就係因為班友推哂個波落前線到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(轉移話題)︰總之香港邊個做特首都死啦，一係大陸直接全面收返香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰哦好呀，即係迫到外資全面徹離香港，大陸放棄開放金融巿場，倒退到變返70年代咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰係呀，遲早都係咁架啦，遲早都係咁架啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰大陸佬呢幾十年賺埋賺埋咁多錢，個個官都賺幾百億，會肯倒退返到以前咁？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰就乜出奇啫，而家已經係咁搬緊d錢走啦佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰咁你早排叫我買嗰層樓, 之後咪要跌到仆街？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />︰(無再出聲)<br />\n<br />\n而家好似覺得自己頭先串咗少少...."},{"pid":"31a549203c2bf47dede90bfc180c5d4e3f5e876d","tid":1229933,"uid":248960,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"加句 happy father's day"},{"pid":"50c140bdb68eb7a3bed8e3fb771887c6616c1459","tid":1229933,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31a549203c2bf47dede90bfc180c5d4e3f5e876d","tid":1229933,"uid":248960,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"加句 happy father's day"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"好彩之前慶祝咗..如果唔係仲尷尬..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c79311c51e3852927cd6cb4d9fb96e00c0d7380","tid":1229933,"uid":74172,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:34:47.000Z","msg":"香港人 影響到自己利益先會收聲"},{"pid":"278d43fc3cdb04584e17ec5ae5b3f9ccc505f53c","tid":1229933,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:35:16.000Z","msg":"美中和好未呀柒頭三毛"},{"pid":"1f25191d93ef7b3083a185f5172488e3f467ab22","tid":1229933,"uid":176888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:36:31.000Z","msg":"唔洗串佢, 快快上街,佢睇到就明白了"},{"pid":"ad8f39687cd8cc4a33249f7327b7aedd83bcde09","tid":1229933,"uid":94600,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"同你一樣, 我老母講咩企最前$5000 1日, 企後面就$1000 1日. 我問佢邊到聽返黎, 就話人地講. <br />\n <br />\n痴痴地, 人地講咩就信, 我問佢, 人地講你個仔係殺人犯既話, 你係唔係都信? 佢就發脾氣<br />\n<br />\n事後有D後悔, 因為老人家都預左沒思考都判斷既能力, 我唔應該怪佢..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029279fa279f2348f5f96d7723f4674db656aaa8","tid":1229933,"uid":149494,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"ad8f39687cd8cc4a33249f7327b7aedd83bcde09